text: Josef Čtvrtníček (born 23 February 1990) is a Czech football player who currently plays for Loko Vltavín. ==Career== In November 2017, joined Čtvrtníček Slavoj Vyšehrad.SK Benátky | FK Slavoj Vyšehrad - SK Benátky‚ kopanabenatky.cz, 11 November 2017 After the season, he then joined FK Zbuzany 1953.
